        </div>

        <h2 id="examples">Real GBP category examples</h2>
        <p>Three real category decisions and the outcomes.</p>

        <h3>1. Dental practice hierarchy</h3>
        <div class="url-flow">
          <span class="uf-label">Primary:</span> <span class="uf-new">Dentist</span><br>
          <span class="uf-label">Secondary:</span> Cosmetic Dentist, Teeth Whitening Service, Dental Implants Provider<br>
          <span class="uf-comment"># Ranks for "dentist near me" and cosmetic queries</span>
        </div>

        <h3>2. HVAC with multi-trade services</h3>
        <div class="url-flow">
          <span class="uf-label">Primary:</span> <span class="uf-new">HVAC Contractor</span><br>
          <span class="uf-label">Secondary:</span> Plumber, Electrician<br>
          <span class="uf-comment"># HVAC drives core rankings; secondaries capture related jobs</span>
        </div>

