              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. You must choose from Google\u2019s fixed list of roughly 4,000 predefined categories. If your business type is not on the list, pick the closest match.</p></div></div>
